ARTICLE.TITLE: Highway 44 Construction Work in Guthrie County should be completed in a Couple of Weeks
ARTICLE.TEXT:
(Guthrie Center) With cold weather right around the corner, construction crews are hustling to put the final touches on road construction projects.

Scott Suhr District Planner for the District 4 Office in southwest Iowa says the patching project on Highway 44 in Guthrie County should wrap up in a couple of weeks.

The project between Guthrie Center and Highway 71, is controlled by flaggers and a pilot car.
